abstract: Parliamentary investigation said to be prompted by strong real estate sales to Chinese.
snippet: Parliamentary investigation said to be prompted by strong real estate sales to Chinese.
lead_paragraph: Middle-class and first-time buyers are being pushed out of Australiaâ€™s booming housing market, a situation that has prompted a parliamentary review of foreign investment laws to determine whether the recent wave of overseas buyers are contributing to rising prices.

lead_paragraph: OPENING OF LUNA PARK (Sunday) Veterans of the Cyclone roller coaster â€” and those who appreciate it best while standing on terra firma â€” will cheer as Luna Park kicks off another season in Coney Island, Brooklyn, starting at noon. An egg-cream splash on the venerable roller coaster, which turns 87 in June, will set it and the other attractions at the amusement park in motion once again.

abstract: Full Bunny Contact, a new Easter-themed carnival on the Lower East Side, offers strategic combat with people dressed up like rabbits, a booth where you can dunk Jesus, and more.
snippet: Full Bunny Contact, a new Easter-themed carnival on the Lower East Side, offers strategic combat with people dressed up like rabbits, a booth where you can dunk Jesus, and more.
lead_paragraph: TIMOTHY HASKELL, he of the slightly twisted imagination who regularly scares people as the creator and director of the â€œNightmareâ€œ haunted houses in New York around Halloween, has something new and a bit less diabolical planned for Easter weekend: Full Bunny Contact, a carnival more focused on fun than on fright.
